"S:"
]
},
" “I am calling about Mrs. ___ with concerns about new hypoxemia.”"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"56e643",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"b",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"B:"
]
},
" “She is postop day 2 after total knee replacement and has not had an O",
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sub",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"2"
]
},
" requirement. After dinner, the O",
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"2"
]
},
" sat was 87% on room air. Patient is alert with some respiratory distress and wheezes on examination. Other vital signs were normal.”"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"b9c2a9",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"b",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"A:"
]
},
" “I am worried about aspiration pneumonia.”"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"edf2f3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"b",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"R:"
]
},
" “I think the patient needs evaluation and possible chest x-ray.”"
]
},
" "
]
}
